WEBVTT

00:00:05.440 --> 00:00:08.360
NETFLIX 原创剧集

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:29.000
剧名：潘达斯奈基

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:36.520
（1984年7月9日）

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:10.000
吃早餐吗？
Breakfast?

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:17.480
你的茶
Here's your tea.

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:25.680
都不说声谢谢
"Thanks, Dad."

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:29.960
抱歉 在想其他事情 需要为今天准备就绪
Sorry. Sorry, I was miles away. Got to get everything ready for today.

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:32.040
跟一些搞电脑的家伙？
This with some computer people?

00:01:32.120 --> 00:01:35.960
对 塔克软件 他们做科林·里特曼的游戏
Yeah. Tuckersoft. They do Colin Ritman's games.

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:38.560
不会是那个著名的科林·里特曼吧
Oh, not the Colin Ritman.

00:01:40.880 --> 00:01:42.240
公司主人塔克尔先生
Mr. Thakur, the owner,

00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:44.080
说我可以演示一下潘达斯奈基
said I could show them my Bandersnatch demo.

00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:47.120
-潘达什么？  -潘达斯奈基
-Your Bander-what?  -Bandersnatch.

00:01:47.480 --> 00:01:48.920
我是根据一本书改编的
I've based it on the book.

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:50.280
（《潘达斯奈基》 杰罗姆·F·戴维斯著）

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:51.600
是你母亲的书吧？
Was that your mother's?

00:01:53.440 --> 00:01:55.360
对 在她的东西里面
It was in her things, yeah.

00:01:56.920 --> 00:01:59.400
-不知道她读没读过  -应该没有
-Don't know if she read it though.  -Don't think so.

00:01:59.480 --> 00:02:02.400
“杰罗姆·F·戴维斯”
"Jerome F. Davies."

00:02:03.800 --> 00:02:05.360
肯定不是一位好作家
Well, he can't be a great writer.

00:02:05.440 --> 00:02:07.280
你一直都在跳来跳去地看
You're always flicking backwards and forwards in that.

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:09.120
不是的 这本书是“选择自己的冒险”
No, it's a "Choose Your Own Adventure" book.

00:02:10.200 --> 00:02:13.000
你来决定你的角色怎么做
You decide what your character does.

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:15.080
像游戏一样
-You know, like a game.  -Sounds thrilling.

00:02:15.160 --> 00:02:16.120
听着挺让人激动

00:02:16.600 --> 00:02:20.120
你来决定早餐想吃什么 如何？
How about you decide what you want for your breakfast?

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:21.160
（白糖沙翁 香甜玉米片）

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:28.400
两种我都觉得太小儿科 但你肯定坚持要吃
Both seem a bit kiddywink to me, but you will insist.

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:40.840
喂
Oi!

00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:45.760
回隔壁屋去！
Get back next door!

00:02:47.160 --> 00:02:49.440
是隔壁那条该死的猎犬
The bloody hound from next door.

00:02:49.640 --> 00:02:50.760
走啊
Go on!

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:52.960
真是烦死人了
Be the death of us.

00:03:13.120 --> 00:03:19.080
（汤姆森双胞胎乐团《入沟》 《这才叫音乐·二》）

00:03:45.720 --> 00:03:47.720
（朋友）

00:04:00.200 --> 00:04:01.800
（塔克软件）
Hello, Tuckersoft.

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:05.440
漂亮 干得好 萨特帕尔
Oh, beautiful. Nice one, Satpal.

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:09.880
去买本森香烟 还有巧克力棒
Alright, fetch us 20 B&amp;H, would you? And... Lion bar.

00:04:10.680 --> 00:04:11.720
好孩子
Good boy.

00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:15.760
你就是斯蒂文
You... are... Steven.

00:04:15.840 --> 00:04:17.200
-是斯蒂芬  -斯蒂芬 抱歉
-Stefan.  -Stefan, sorry, mate.

00:04:17.280 --> 00:04:18.400
没事 大家总是会叫错
That's alright. I get it all the time.

00:04:18.680 --> 00:04:20.640
抱歉有点乱 我们周一刚搬来
Sorry about the chaos. We just moved in Monday.

00:04:21.320 --> 00:04:22.560
地方很大
It's big.

00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:25.040
扩张 就是我的计划
Well, expansion, that's my plan.

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:28.680
想想 一整个团队 只做图像
Imagine, OK. A whole team just for graphics,

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.080
这边团队做声音 那边做情节
another for sound, for gameplay.

00:04:31.240 --> 00:04:35.400
我们会成为热门产品工厂 就像电脑游戏界的摩城唱片
We're going to be a hit factory. Like Motown but for computer games.

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:37.560
这话 你是第一个听到的人
You heard it here first.

00:04:37.720 --> 00:04:39.720
（金属头）

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:42.520
这是科林的新作
That's Colin's new one.

00:04:44.120 --> 00:04:46.640
-科林·里特曼？  -他就在那
-Colin Ritman?  -That's him over there.

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:50.840
太疯狂了 他的游戏我都玩过
That's crazy. I've played all of his games.

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:52.040
去打个招呼吧
Let's say hello.

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:54.840
-他在工作 确定他不介意吗？  -没事的
-Sure he won't mind? He's working.  -He'll be fine. He'll be fine. Shh! Shh!

00:04:57.440 --> 00:04:58.720
等等
Oh. Wait, wait, wait.

00:05:00.600 --> 00:05:02.360
听什么呢 卡加咕咕乐团？
What's this, Kajagoogoo?

00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:06.000
怎么可能
You wish.

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:09.240
看看他这状态 今年赚的钱都够买兰博基尼了
The state of him, he's made enough this year to buy a Lamborghini

00:05:09.320 --> 00:05:11.120
但还是抽自己卷的烟
and he still smokes roll-ups.

00:05:11.200 --> 00:05:14.840
外面卖的卷烟都有士的宁 闹笑话的人是他
Well, pre-rolled has strychnine in them, so the joke's on him.

00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:18.000
随便了 这位是斯蒂芬…
Anyway, this is Stefan, er...

00:05:18.520 --> 00:05:19.960
巴特勒
Butler, Butler.

00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:24.320
我是科林
I'm Colin, yeah?

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:27.640
嗯 我玩过你所有游戏 全部所有
Yeah, I've played all of your games. All of them.

00:05:27.960 --> 00:05:31.320
除了康懋达电脑上的那些 我没有康懋达电脑
Except the Commodore ones, I don't... don't have a Commodore.

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:36.280
-康懋达电脑声卡不错  -是啊
Great sound chip, the Commodore. Yeah.

00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:39.200
这是我最新的游戏
This is my latest.

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:40.320
（运行）

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:46.040
叫鼻子跳水
It's called Nohzdyve.

00:05:51.640 --> 00:05:55.360
-游戏界面真流畅  -花了一些功夫
-The sprites are so smooth.  -That took some doing.

00:05:58.040 --> 00:05:59.440
