The eyeballs have overrun the video memory--

00:06:05.080 --> 00:06:08.280
是啊 显存 我正要说呢
Oh, yeah, video memory, yeah. I was going to say that.

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:10.240
这样 说正经事吧
Anyway, listen, let's get down to business.

00:06:10.320 --> 00:06:12.720
斯蒂芬要给我们演示点东西
Stefan's got something to demo for us.

00:06:13.720 --> 00:06:15.440
厉害了
Bloody hell.

00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:19.160
就像三维怪物迷宫？
So it's like 3D Monster Maze?

00:06:19.240 --> 00:06:21.040
不过人是在不断进行选择
Only when you're moving from choice to choice.

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:24.240
-其实是一个探险游戏  -像《霍比特人》
-It's actually an adventure game.  -Like The Hobbit?

00:06:24.360 --> 00:06:27.320
