Yeah, but... without any typing.

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:29.240
不用打字？
Without any typing?

00:06:29.320 --> 00:06:32.600
-所以不会有“找灯”什么的？  -对
So no "get lamp" or whatever? That's right.

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:43.080
屏幕上出现选择 倒计时内确定就行
Choices come up on the screen and you pick one against the clock.

00:06:43.160 --> 00:06:44.600
（弱小的人类 要崇拜我吗？）

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:47.560
他是恶魔帕克斯 是书里的
OK, he's Pax, he's the demon. He's in the book.

00:06:47.760 --> 00:06:49.440
我们其实到了一个选择点
So we've actually arrived at a choice point,

00:06:49.520 --> 00:06:51.360
用游戏杆进行选择
and then you can choose with the joystick.

00:06:51.440 --> 00:06:52.960
有十秒时间
You've got ten seconds.

00:06:53.560 --> 00:06:54.600
崇拜他
Worship him.

00:06:54.760 --> 00:06:57.040
不要这样 他是命运的窃贼…
No, don't do that, he's the Thief of Destiny...

00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:58.320
我是说 在书里
in the book, I mean.

00:06:59.400 --> 00:07:01.920
我家里有一本 但从没读过
Got a copy of this at home. Never got around to reading it.

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:04.840
你应该读读 杰罗姆·戴维斯是天才
You should. Jerome F. Davies was a genius.

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:07.560
他不是发疯了 砍下了妻子的头吗？
Didn't he go bonkers and cut his wife's head off?

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:09.880
-是 但我是说除了这点之外…  -不好意思
-Yeah, but, I mean, apart from that-- -Excuse me.

00:07:11.480 --> 00:07:12.320
（崇拜帕克斯）

00:07:13.040 --> 00:07:13.880
（超出范围）

