怎么回事？
What's happened?

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:17.640
这条路的程序我还没写
Well, I haven't programmed that pathway yet.

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:19.120
有很多条路？
Lot of paths then?

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:23.320
嗯 如果按书里来 就会这样
Well, yeah, if it's going to be like the book.

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:25.560
那你打算怎么办？
So, come on. How do you want to go about this?

00:07:27.200 --> 00:07:30.520
-你感兴趣？  -当然啊
-You're... you're interested?  -That's what I'm saying.

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:33.240
现在是七月 如果要冲击圣诞节
OK, it's July now, so if we want to hit Christmas,

00:07:33.320 --> 00:07:35.880
那我们在十一月就要投入生产
then we'll need the tapes in Smiths by November.

00:07:35.960 --> 00:07:39.760
我的提议是 你来这里写程序
OK. So here's my proposal. Come and write it here.

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:42.080
-这里？  -对啊
-Here?  -Yeah!

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:45.840
我们专门为你安排几张桌子 建一个小团队
We'll give you a couple of desks, set up a small team, just for you.

00:07:46.280 --> 00:07:48.000
当然 科林也在附近
And of course Col's on hand.

00:07:48.520 --> 00:07:49.760
你怎么想？
What do you reckon?

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:53.280
对了 我下周会雇用一个做声卡的
Oh, and hey, I'm hiring this sound chip guy next week,

00:07:53.360 --> 00:07:56.160
所以音乐我们可以解决 全在公司内部做
so music we can take care of. All in-house.

00:07:56.320 --> 00:07:58.560
