So, come on. What's your answer?

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:03.960
好
Yes.

00:08:05.400 --> 00:08:06.600
完美
Perfect. Perfect.

00:08:06.680 --> 00:08:09.720
好 第一件事就是稍微精简一下项目
OK, so the first thing we need to do is streamline the project a little.

00:08:09.880 --> 00:08:12.720
