We can't fit a breeze block of a book into 48K.

00:08:16.920 --> 00:08:19.120
看呐
Oh, look at this.

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:21.560
给
Here you go.

00:08:22.040 --> 00:08:24.080
祝我生日快乐
Happy Birthday to me.

00:08:26.760 --> 00:08:29.120
抱歉 哥们 选错路了
Sorry, mate. Wrong path.

00:08:33.480 --> 00:08:34.320
