Oof, well, maybe next week we'll have something more for you...

00:09:18.520 --> 00:09:20.400
那孩子什么都不懂
That kid knows nothing.

00:09:21.960 --> 00:09:23.360
我应该再试一次
I should try again.

00:09:28.680 --> 00:09:30.840
