怎么回事？
What's happened?

01:35:27.200 --> 01:35:29.240
这条路的程序我还没写
Well, I haven't programmed that pathway yet.

01:35:29.320 --> 01:35:30.160
有很多条路？
Lot of paths then?

01:35:31.680 --> 01:35:34.760
嗯 如果按书里来 就会这样
Well, yeah, if it's going to be like the book.

01:35:35.520 --> 01:35:37.760
那你打算怎么办？
So, come on. How do you want to go about this?

01:35:39.040 --> 01:35:42.160
-你感兴趣？  -当然啊
