复制不够快 人人都想要科林·里特曼的游戏
We can't dupe them fast enough. Everybody wants a bit of Colin Ritman.

01:45:23.080 --> 01:45:26.200
-科林呢？  -鬼知道 逃班了
-Where is Colin?  -God knows. He's gone AWOL.

01:45:26.280 --> 01:45:27.680
人没来 电话也不接
He hasn't come in, answered his phone. Par for the course from him.

01:45:28.040 --> 01:45:29.360
他这样也不是一次两次了

01:45:29.440 --> 01:45:31.440
大概去阿姆斯特丹找园艺地点了
Probably fucked off to Amsterdam for a spot of gardening.

01:45:31.520 --> 01:45:34.040
他会回来的 总是如此
He'll be back, he always is. Anyway, come on.

01:45:44.240 --> 01:45:47.800
看着不错 好在我把广告加倍了
Looking good. Good thing I doubled on the advertising.

01:45:49.840 --> 01:45:51.280
（特工对你产生了怀疑）

01:45:51.360 --> 01:45:52.560
（后退  杀死特工）

01:45:54.640 --> 01:45:55.960
这不是…
That's not...

01:45:56.040 --> 01:45:58.760
斯蒂芬 今天交工 你之前说很稳定的
Stefan, mate. This is due today. You said it was stable.

01:45:58.840 --> 01:46:00.840
-之前是的 只是…  -只是什么？
-It was, I just-- -Just what?

01:46:01.360 --> 01:46:02.440
我新加了一条路线
I added in a new path,

01:46:02.520 --> 01:46:05.200
政府阴谋分支 我以为这样就没有漏洞了
the government conspiracy branch, I thought I'd tied up all the loose ends.

01:46:05.280 --> 01:46:06.600
这是你新加的 拿掉不就好了
If it's something you've added, let's just take it out.

01:46:06.680 --> 01:46:08.920
-不行 它很重要  -斯蒂芬
-No, it's important.  -Stefan, mate.

01:46:09.680 --> 01:46:11.040
交付日是今天
The deadline is today.

01:46:11.120 --> 01:46:14.120
给我这个周末就行 我一定能把新路线加进去
I just need the weekend. I know I can squeeze this path in.

01:46:14.560 --> 01:46:17.360
-游戏已经足够复杂了  -就这个周末 拜托了
-It's complicated enough.  -Just the weekend. Please.

01:46:21.160 --> 01:46:22.720
-周一一早给我  -一定
-First thing Monday.  -First thing.

01:46:23.160 --> 01:46:27.160
我得赶快走了 要见约翰孟席斯公司的人
OK. Shit, I've got to run, meeting the John Menzies guys.

01:46:27.240 --> 01:46:30.840
千万别搞砸了 这项目现在十分紧要
Just don't fuck up. There's a lot riding on this now.

01:46:31.000 --> 01:46:32.000
